Philippine Long Distance Telephone Cosaid it has called a special shareholder meeting to approve aproposed two-for-one stock split and a 20 pct stock dividend.    The company said the meeting will be held July 15 andshareholders of record on April 27 will be eligible to vote.    The company said it will also ask shareholders to approvean increase in authorized common shares to 134 mln and ofserial preferred stock to 383 mln and to authorize the sale oftwo billion pesos of debentures. Reuter&#3;